Subject: RE: [VB] firewall grommets

  I take a piece of 6 mm fuel hose and split it, wrap it around the fuel
line, push it through the hole and use a hose clamp on each end to keep it
from moving. It also makes it a lot easier to push the fuel hose on.

ronnie

